    <thetext>The capability of showing different requirements was added recently, where command &apos;--requires&apos; shows packages needed for instalation and &apos;--requires-pre&apos; shows packages needed for running of package.

``--requires`` - Display capabilities that the package depends on. Same as ``--qf &quot;%{requires}&quot;``.

``--requires-pre``- Display capabilities that the package depends on for running a ``%pre`` script (Same as ``--qf &quot;%{requires-pre}&quot;``).</thetext>
